# README #

1) Run cloud orchestrator on the machine witch access to LXC container image with thingspeak service
# iot_fwd.py

2) Install required Python packages:
# apt-get install python-pip python-dev
# pip install ryu repoze.lru stevedore greenlet pyyaml scapy

This code has been tested using Ryu version 3.26, more recent versions of Ryu may not work.

3) In one terminal, start Ryu with novi_rest_iot_app.py application
$ ryu-manager novi_rest_iot_app.py